xwikidoc.title: Geographical Regions of Erithnoi
xwikidoc.content:
[[[[image:Erithnoi_Large.png||alt="Erithnoi and Surrounding lands of Ergh" style="float: right;" width="500"]]>>attach:Erithnoi_Large.png||title="(click for full size image)"]]
* [[Kinergh>>doc:Kinergh]] - A small kingdom to the northeast of Gilduin. * [[Elfan Holds>>doc:ElfanHolds]] - The ancient lands of the elves in Erithnoi. * [[Holburgs>>doc:Holburgs]] - A mountainous upland area on western border of Kinergh centered on the dwarven city of Dalcaroth. * [[The Melthian Mountains>>doc:MelthianMountains]] - A mighty mountain range to the north of Kinergh. * [[Vye-Elek>>doc:Vye-Elek]] - A small barony north of the Holburgs. * [[The Midrealms>>doc:Midrealms]] - A chaotic area to the east of the Elfan Holds. * [[Othan>>doc:Othan]] - A mighty human nation on the east coast of Erithnoi. * [[Gilduin>>doc:Gilduin]] - A wartorn kingdom on the western borders of Erithnoi. * [[Khem>>doc:Khem]] - A land of nomads to the west of Gilduin. * [[Sildune>>doc:Sildune]] - A wild land north of the Midrealms which is sparsely inhabited and subject to humanoid incursions. * [[Great Boreal Forest>>doc:GreatBorealForest]] - A vast northern forest spanning the whole northern part of Erithnoi. * [[Ta-Al-Erg>>doc:Ta-Al-Erg]] - The Middle Sea to the south of Erithnoi. * [[Kazan>>doc:Kazan]] - A land in the far northeast of Erithnoi where doughty warriors battle giants. * [[Kanth>>doc:Kanth]] - The southeastern corner of Erithnoi. This land contains strong orc tribes and small human kingdoms. * [[Principality of Ek>>doc:PrincipalityOfEk]] - A land to the south of Gilduin which is ruled by the Grey Order of Mages. * [[Eldoran Isles>>doc:EldoranIsles]] - A pair of islands along the south coast of Gilduin known for their pirates and other strange and magical things.
